<i>noun</i>: 화 [화ː], 진노 [진노], 열 [열], 약 [약], 악 [악], 뿔 [뿔], 분노심 [분ː노심], 분노 [분ː노], 노발대발 [노ː발대발], 격분 [격뿐], 격노 [경노] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>화 [화ː]</dt><br>
<dd>anger; fury</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 못마땅하거나 노여워하는 감정.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of strong frustration or anger.</dd><br>
<dt>진노 [진노]</dt><br>
<dd>rage; fury; anger; wrath</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 화를 내며 노여워함. 또는 그런 감정.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being enraged and frustrated, or such a feeling.</dd><br>
<dt>열 [열]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fever</dd><br>
<dd>아플 때 몸에 생기는 더운 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>A hot sensation that occurs when one is sick.</dd><br>
<dd>2. heat</dd><br>
<dd>뜨겁게 만드는 에너지.</dd><br>
<dd>An energy that causes something to become hot.</dd><br>
<dd>3. energy; hard work; effort</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 다하는 정성.</dd><br>
<dd>The devotion that one gives to something.</dd><br>
<dd>4. rage; fury; anger</dd><br>
<dd>매우 화가 나거나 흥분한 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being furious or agitated.</dd><br>
<dt>약 [약]</dt><br>
<dd>1. anger; fury</dd><br>
<dd>놀림을 받거나 하여 화가 나는 감정.</dd><br>
<dd>The feeling of anger from being ridiculed, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. height</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 식물이 한창 자랄 때 생기는 맵거나 쓴 자극적인 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>The strong, spicy or bitter quality that a plant develops when it is in the midst of a growth spurt.</dd><br>
<dt>악 [악]</dt><br>
<dd>anger; fury</dd><br>
<dd>있는 힘을 다하여 마구 쓰는 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>What energy that one musters up and uses to the fullest.</dd><br>
<dt>뿔 [뿔]</dt><br>
<dd>anger; fury</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 기분이 나쁘거나 화가 나고 분한 감정.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) A bad, angry, and furious feeling.</dd><br>
<dt>분노심 [분ː노심]</dt><br>
<dd>rage; fury</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 화가 난 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of strong anger.</dd><br>
<dt>분노 [분ː노]</dt><br>
<dd>rage; fury</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 화를 냄.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being very angry.</dd><br>
<dt>노발대발 [노ː발대발]</dt><br>
<dd>wild rage; fury</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 화를 냄.</dd><br>
<dd>Becoming extremely angry.</dd><br>
<dt>격분 [격뿐]</dt><br>
<dd>rage; violent anger; fury</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 화를 냄.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of extreme anger.</dd><br>
<dt>격노 [경노]</dt><br>
<dd>rage; fury; violent anger; wrath; exasperation</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 화를 냄.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of extreme anger.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>